00:21:53.600 --> 00:21:53.920
But I could feel the atmosphere again, and I thought that was interesting.

00:21:53.920 --> 00:22:01.031
I see these events, and the Lord showed me even with British Columbia again, I saw a major earthquake again in British Columbia.

00:22:05.840 --> 00:22:06.251
That's why I kept seeing this, and the Lord told me, 'This is going to happen.

00:22:06.251 --> 00:22:08.034
These major shakings are going to happen.

00:22:08.034 --> 00:22:15.131
' And he highlighted the Olympics in February, and it's in Italy, and he said, 'Pray over this.

00:22:21.247 --> 00:22:21.695
This is something you need to pray over.

00:22:25.600 --> 00:22:25.899
The Olympics in 2026.

00:22:25.899 --> 00:22:27.700
Pray over the Winter Olympics in Italy.

00:22:27.700 --> 00:22:28.606
It's something serious.

00:22:28.606 --> 00:22:36.440
' He hasn't shown me, and he said, 'I'll give you more to the puzzle as you go.

00:22:36.440 --> 00:22:37.703
I'll give you more.

00:22:37.703 --> 00:22:48.880
It's like taking a piece of the pie, and he gives you a little more and he gives you a little more whenever you're able to chew it because he doesn't want to give it all to you because you'd choke on it.

00:22:48.880 --> 00:22:51.919
He gives you a little bit more and a little bit more.

00:22:51.919 --> 00:22:55.828
' And I think it's amazing how the Lord talks to me.

00:22:57.339 --> 00:22:57.600
I say, 'Lord, thank you.

00:22:57.600 --> 00:22:59.920
Well, that's what I can have today.

00:22:59.920 --> 00:23:01.200
Okay, I'm appreciative.

00:23:01.200 --> 00:23:04.899
' But either way, Lord, we're going to keep praying this out.

00:23:08.719 --> 00:23:09.359
We're going to see what you have for us each and every single day.

00:23:12.340 --> 00:23:13.170
But as we pray into this, I saw, like I said, the Ronald Reagan face on Trump.

00:23:17.253 --> 00:23:17.547
I saw him excited about the golden street, saying, 'Oh, look at this.

00:23:17.547 --> 00:23:20.951
' You know how he talks, 'Praise him, I'm going to make America huge.

00:23:20.951 --> 00:23:22.747
It's going to be great.

00:23:22.747 --> 00:23:26.560
' You know, and he's so excited about the golden street.

00:23:43.379 --> 00:23:43.719
But the Lord said, 'Notice the foundation for the body of Christ is really thin there.

00:23:44.740 --> 00:23:51.840
It's not, you know, he's not making America great again; it's to make America have a time of, "Let's fill our pockets.

00:23:51.840 --> 00:23:53.303
Let's get ready.

00:23:53.303 --> 00:24:02.240
"' Listen to him, listen to the Spirit of the Lord so that you know how to get through the days ahead.

00:24:06.126 --> 00:24:06.434
And people say, 'Well, I thought Kim Clement prophesied this and that.

00:24:06.434 --> 00:24:13.714
' Kim Clement saw a lot of darkness that he never spoke about because he was always telling you there was another side of it.

00:24:23.460 --> 00:24:24.710
Just like what he talked about Joseph; Kim Clement got into Joseph, and he said Joseph prepared for the storm so that he didn't have to go through the darkness.

00:24:24.710 --> 00:24:29.240
It wasn't for the body of Christ, and I agree with Kim Clement wholeheartedly.

00:24:29.240 --> 00:24:35.520
What I told you was coming is not for you.

00:24:35.520 --> 00:24:50.940
You are to be the salt and the light of all the darkness, all the shaking to awaken, and all the stuff that I've seen about the plague, the pestilence, the financial crisis, and all the tribulation stuff that I've seen coming—earthquakes in divers places.

00:24:50.940 --> 00:24:53.138
Ladies and gentlemen, we are the bride of Christ.

00:24:53.138 --> 00:24:55.179
We are the salt and light of this earth.

00:24:55.179 --> 00:24:57.143
We are the head and not the tail.

00:24:57.143 --> 00:24:58.760
We're above and not beneath.

00:24:58.760 --> 00:25:00.754
We'll go through and not go under.

00:25:00.754 --> 00:25:04.941
That's what the Bible says, and I line up with the word of God.

00:25:04.941 --> 00:25:09.429
I told Diana, 'We will not participate in financial destitution; we've lived that, and I know I'm not going back down that road.

00:25:09.429 --> 00:25:12.039
' So I'm asking the Father already, 'Babe, let's pray.

00:25:12.039 --> 00:25:24.995
Let's pray into this, that we are in the right place at the right time doing exactly what the Lord has asked us to do, that we are hearing what he's saying so that we can get what is out of his hand.

00:25:24.995 --> 00:25:31.240
' I don't want to be a person that's in the middle of Sodom and Gomorrah going, 'You know what?

00:25:32.360 --> 00:25:34.608
I like it over here too much, and I'm not hearing what's coming.

00:25:34.608 --> 00:25:40.919
' And many of you all are so close to Sodom and Gomorrah, you don't know what's coming.

00:25:43.771 --> 00:25:53.051
And I'm thankful that you're here, but like I said, there's so much static in the atmosphere with prophet so-and-so saying this and prophet so-and-so saying that, and you're going, 'Well, Brandon, you said that.

00:25:53.051 --> 00:25:53.600
How?

00:25:53.600 --> 00:25:55.713
' and you're trying to copy the word.

00:25:55.713 --> 00:25:58.880
Folks, if you realize, I ain't trying to toot my own horn.

00:25:58.880 --> 00:26:03.702
I said it months ago, and you're hearing it from them, and you're saying, 'He's the original voice.

00:26:03.702 --> 00:26:05.306
' No, no, no.

00:26:05.306 --> 00:26:07.982
The original voice started with us, and it's usually copied.

00:26:14.914 --> 00:26:15.131
But I don't point it out.

00:26:23.980 --> 00:26:24.190
I just keep going because it's not maturity to do that, to go, 'Well, you know, they're copying.

00:26:24.190 --> 00:26:26.019
' Just grow up, who cares?

00:26:29.440 --> 00:26:32.114
But I'm going to tell you, stay on the vine, hear God for yourself.

00:26:32.114 --> 00:26:37.279
Bottom line: you don't need me, you don't need them, you need God.

00:26:45.440 --> 00:26:45.640
And who's saying it first, who cares?

00:26:55.909 --> 00:26:56.331
It's about Jesus.

00:26:56.331 --> 00:26:58.110
That's what he told me.

00:26:58.110 --> 00:27:00.400
He said, 'Brandon, don't lose track of all that stuff.

00:27:00.400 --> 00:27:02.040
Just keep close to me.

00:27:02.040 --> 00:27:04.200
All this other stuff will work itself out.

00:27:04.200 --> 00:27:06.240
' Who's saying what, he's already told you all that.

00:27:06.240 --> 00:27:10.340
There's a lot of static in the air and there's a lot of all this weirdness, flakiness—'We're going home, we're doing this.

00:27:10.340 --> 00:27:13.404
' I'm like, 'No, just focus on the task at hand.

00:27:13.404 --> 00:27:16.862
' You know why I'm not worried about the rapture of the church?

00:27:18.114 --> 00:27:18.342
Because I occupy until he comes.

00:27:18.342 --> 00:27:19.520
I'm too busy occupying.

00:27:19.520 --> 00:27:22.620
I'm too busy trying to take the land for Jesus.

00:27:22.620 --> 00:27:23.991
I'm not worried about the rapture.

00:27:25.609 --> 00:27:25.840
You know why?

00:27:34.450 --> 00:27:34.620
Because I believe I qualify; my lamp's full of oil.

00:27:34.620 --> 00:27:35.507
Stay ready.

00:27:48.868 --> 00:27:49.291
I'm staying ready every day.

00:27:49.291 --> 00:27:51.263
I'm looking for it.

00:27:51.263 --> 00:27:53.520
Diana and I are looking for him.

00:27:53.520 --> 00:27:56.986
We're looking up like this and we say, 'Hey babe, let's pray today.

00:27:56.986 --> 00:28:00.587
' We're looking up, we're taking communion, and we're seeking him as a family.

00:28:05.919 --> 00:28:06.259
And I'm not worried about when he's coming.

00:28:06.259 --> 00:28:14.900
I'm just doing everything I can to catch all the people I can around me on fire for him so that their vessels are full, too.

00:28:14.900 --> 00:28:19.644
But if you're always looking up and not helping those around you, what are we here for?

00:28:19.644 --> 00:28:22.480
'We're rapture-bound, we're out of here, God come and get us.

00:28:22.480 --> 00:28:28.056
' And we're always looking up, but you have all these people dying and going to hell, all of them.

00:28:29.550 --> 00:28:38.020
And that's why I try to tell you all every single time when we come on here: you need to get your heart right before Jesus Christ because I'm staying vertical.

00:28:39.760 --> 00:28:39.947
I keep my eyes on him.

00:28:39.947 --> 00:28:43.919
I don't go horizontal, looking at when is the rapture coming.

00:28:52.605 --> 00:28:52.937
It doesn't matter.

00:29:04.880 --> 00:29:05.040
I occupy until he comes.

00:29:12.229 --> 00:29:12.399
My heart's longing for him.

00:29:12.399 --> 00:29:16.139
I've been on the other side; I've seen what he has for us.

00:29:16.139 --> 00:29:21.049
I've had amazing visitations of heaven, but I'm telling you, it's not my focus.

00:29:21.049 --> 00:29:28.960
My focus is the job at hand: to bring in the lost as quickly as I can because they're going to burn in hell.

00:29:31.424 --> 00:29:34.480
And what's most precious to him is precious to me—the soul of man.

00:29:34.480 --> 00:29:38.439
What's precious to him is to see that none should perish, that all come to repentance.

00:29:39.740 --> 00:29:43.246
And all the other stuff is going to work itself out because I'm keeping my eyes on him.

00:29:43.246 --> 00:29:50.480
The rapture of the church can happen whenever it needs to happen, but right now, I'm focused on the task at hand.

00:30:01.679 --> 00:30:01.983
I'm not worried about my problems or overcoming or Megan or anything.

00:30:04.480 --> 00:30:16.399
I'm focused on just getting as many of you all saved that I can, to tell them that Jesus Christ is coming and you need to repent so that you don't burn in hell for eternity.

00:30:20.379 --> 00:30:20.709
Do you understand?

00:30:20.709 --> 00:30:22.658
All the other stuff is not important.

00:30:23.942 --> 00:30:28.056
The most important thing is that we all know that he is coming.

00:30:28.056 --> 00:30:34.295
We can agree on that, but on timing we might differ, and we can say, 'Is there a reverse rapture?

00:30:34.295 --> 00:30:35.341
' and all this.

00:30:35.341 --> 00:30:39.919
I never even heard where it is; I don't know about all this stuff.

00:30:39.919 --> 00:30:52.550
There are so many people with so many different—'Well, so-and-so said this, there's a reverse rapture, there's a major 9/11 event and all these people are going to die' and all this stuff.

00:30:52.550 --> 00:30:58.045
You can pick anything in the scripture you want to and try to twist it the way you want to make it sound.

00:30:58.045 --> 00:31:07.200
I'm going to tell you this: I'm going to stay grounded, and I'm going to keep getting people saved, and I'm not trying to come up with some crazy theology.

00:31:10.209 --> 00:31:10.399
I don't care.

00:31:10.399 --> 00:31:31.569
I just stay on the Word, telling you that Jesus Christ, in the Great Commission, to go into all the world, lay hands on the sick, cast out devils, raise the dead, to bring sight to the blind, to do everything the Lord told me I could do by His Word, and not get off in la-la land.

00:31:31.569 --> 00:31:37.920
Stay grounded in these last days, because you're going to get swayed by a lot of voices.

00:31:37.920 --> 00:31:45.215
Well, this prophet said there's no more financial blessing, and if you invest in this, you're going to lose everything.

00:31:46.160 --> 00:31:46.880
I don't care what they say.

00:31:47.120 --> 00:31:47.840
You know what?

00:31:47.840 --> 00:31:50.799
I care about what He says.

00:32:02.942 --> 00:32:03.164
And I listen to Him and I say, "Babe, does that witness with you?

00:32:03.164 --> 00:32:04.498
" Ah, don't listen to me.

00:32:04.498 --> 00:32:04.933
Okay.

00:32:04.933 --> 00:32:09.920
Well, let's pray some more until we know that we're hearing, because you don't get off in la-la land, especially when we pray.

00:32:09.920 --> 00:32:12.260
Pray as a family.

00:32:12.260 --> 00:32:12.979
We take communion.

00:32:12.979 --> 00:32:17.938
We believe God that He's going to teach us and guide us into all things.

00:32:20.846 --> 00:32:27.576
And if we miss it, and you fall down and skin your knee, then you pick yourself up and say, "Man, that hurt a little bit, but God, I'm still focused on You.

00:32:27.576 --> 00:32:32.026
" Folks, when you miss it, you don't go, "Well, I'll quit.

00:32:32.026 --> 00:32:37.440
" No, you just keep brushing your knees off, pick your bicycle up, and you keep riding.

00:32:40.920 --> 00:32:41.350
You keep on, keep on.

00:32:41.350 --> 00:32:50.529
But I'm telling you, there's a lot of spiritual weirdness out there right now with all this different stuff going on.

00:32:57.199 --> 00:32:57.439
And well, "I don't know who to believe.

00:32:57.679 --> 00:32:58.651
" I hear that a lot.

00:33:02.524 --> 00:33:02.702
"I don't know who to believe.

00:33:02.702 --> 00:33:03.946
" Well, go with your peace.

00:33:03.946 --> 00:33:04.982
That's a good one.

00:33:06.057 --> 00:33:07.200
And don't listen to me, don't listen to him.

00:33:07.200 --> 00:33:08.579
What does your peace say?

00:33:24.267 --> 00:33:27.669
What do you feel the Holy Ghost telling you?

00:33:43.537 --> 00:33:43.742
And even Diana, we were talking about making a big decision about something.

00:33:57.147 --> 00:33:57.333
And it's not the answer that I wanted, but I said, "Okay, let's pray in the Spirit together.

00:33:57.333 --> 00:34:01.609
" So, I grabbed her hand and we were praying, and she goes, "What do you hear?

00:34:01.609 --> 00:34:03.759
" And I told her what I heard.

00:34:21.070 --> 00:34:21.520
And I said, "What do you hear?

00:34:21.520 --> 00:34:23.005
" She goes like this.

00:34:28.240 --> 00:34:32.739
I said, "It's not what I wanted to hear, and it's not what my spirit wanted, but it's what I have peace about.

00:34:32.739 --> 00:34:34.639
So go with that.

00:34:34.639 --> 00:34:55.243
" Even if my flesh didn't want to hear what I felt like the Holy Spirit just told me, because that's not the answer that I wanted, because sometimes you already have an answer in your mind of what you think you want the Spirit of God to tell you, and you've already made up your mind.

00:34:55.243 --> 00:34:57.652
So you're already decided in your flesh.

00:34:57.652 --> 00:35:03.712
So you bypass the Spirit of God, what He's trying to tell you in your heart.

00:35:10.415 --> 00:35:19.440
And so you're not going to hear the Spirit of God because you so desperately want what you want.

00:35:19.440 --> 00:35:23.546
And it's not going to work that way.

00:35:23.546 --> 00:35:25.940
He'll tell you things that your flesh doesn't like.

00:35:25.940 --> 00:35:27.140
"Brandon, lose weight.

00:35:27.700 --> 00:35:28.480
" I don't like that.

00:35:28.480 --> 00:35:29.952
"Okay, Brandon, you do this.

00:35:29.952 --> 00:35:31.032
" And I'm like, okay.

00:35:31.032 --> 00:35:32.231
"Brandon, stop texting people.

00:35:32.231 --> 00:35:33.333
Stop calling people.

00:35:33.333 --> 00:35:35.120
Brandon, you need to do this.

00:35:48.390 --> 00:35:48.720
" And I go, okay.

00:35:48.720 --> 00:35:50.320
So, I've done that in the past.

00:35:50.320 --> 00:35:52.320
It's hard sometimes when you're social.

00:36:05.573 --> 00:36:05.911
I butterfly about things.

00:36:10.302 --> 00:36:13.538
You want to talk to folks and the Lord says, "Brandon, I don't want you to do that anymore.

00:36:13.538 --> 00:36:13.947
" Okay?

00:36:15.543 --> 00:36:18.720
You know, just me, and I'm just being real with you all.

00:36:20.514 --> 00:36:29.100
But it takes being obedient and willing and saying, "God, I'll eat the fruit of the land, regardless if my flesh likes it or not.

00:36:29.100 --> 00:36:38.440
When You correct me, I want to have ears to hear and a heart to receive what the Spirit is saying, even if my flesh doesn't like it.

00:36:38.440 --> 00:36:43.670
" "Brandon, I want you to stay at this job and clean bathrooms.

00:36:43.670 --> 00:36:44.510
" That's not You.

00:36:44.510 --> 00:36:45.380
That's the devil.

00:36:45.380 --> 00:36:46.690
"Get thee behind me, Satan.

00:36:48.370 --> 00:36:51.280
" And that's what you say.

00:36:51.280 --> 00:36:52.780
"But surely that's not God.

00:36:52.780 --> 00:36:54.240
" Year after year, 15 years.

00:37:05.619 --> 00:37:05.869
And you go, "Lord, is that You still?

00:37:05.869 --> 00:37:06.869
" "Yes, it is.

00:37:06.869 --> 00:37:07.457
Keep going.

00:37:07.964 --> 00:37:10.400
" "I want you to stay in this shotgun house for all these years.

00:37:10.400 --> 00:37:19.623
" 22 years in a shotgun house with barely 800 square feet, with holes in the floor, with a leaky roof, pouring water when it rains, mold growing.

00:37:34.994 --> 00:37:35.257
It was terrible.

00:37:35.257 --> 00:37:36.663
22 years doing it.

00:37:39.599 --> 00:37:39.939
And you sit there and go, "God, can we leave?

00:37:39.939 --> 00:37:40.280
" "No.

00:37:40.280 --> 00:37:41.885
Take care of this, do this.

00:37:50.480 --> 00:37:50.747
" And you go, "Lord, this cannot be You.

00:37:53.430 --> 00:37:54.720
" And the Lord said, "What do you feel, babe?

00:37:54.720 --> 00:38:02.816
" She goes, "I feel like the Lord says we're supposed to stay here 22 years.

00:38:02.816 --> 00:38:08.349
" And you sit there and go, "Lord, this doesn't make any sense.

00:38:08.349 --> 00:38:10.240
Help me with my leaky roof.

00:38:10.240 --> 00:38:13.872
Help me with this.

00:38:25.510 --> 00:38:25.740
" And finally, He sends you a blessing and says, "It's time to move.

00:38:25.740 --> 00:38:26.659
" Do you understand?

00:38:26.659 --> 00:38:33.190
It's not always what your flesh wants to hear when He tells you to do something.

00:38:33.190 --> 00:38:41.059
Sometimes it makes your flesh squirm, but it's being obedient and following that peace that passes all understanding.

00:38:49.303 --> 00:39:00.880
And I'm telling you, Jesus, I'm sure when God said, "You're going to have to die on that cross, Son, and you're going to have to suffer for all these people, and it's going to be probably the worst thing that you ever could imagine, but I need you to do it.

00:39:00.880 --> 00:39:03.900
" I'm sure Jesus was like, "Surely that's not My Father.

00:39:03.900 --> 00:39:11.680
" Seriously, you know, I bet He's thinking that in His mind, "Man, this is going to be...

00:39:11.680 --> 00:39:15.660
if it be Your will, Father, let this cup pass before Me.

00:39:35.017 --> 00:39:35.269
But not My will, but Yours be done.

00:39:37.120 --> 00:39:37.760
" And He said, "I'll die for them.

00:39:37.760 --> 00:39:38.180
" I'm so glad He did.

00:39:38.180 --> 00:39:39.230
Yes, I'm so thankful.

00:39:39.230 --> 00:39:41.463
"It's not my will, but Yours be done, Lord.

00:39:41.463 --> 00:39:42.377
" That's what He said.

00:39:49.380 --> 00:39:49.680
"I choose today to take on sickness.

00:39:59.340 --> 00:39:59.480
I choose today to take on their pain.

00:40:12.000 --> 00:40:12.440
I choose today to bear their sin.

00:40:15.582 --> 00:40:15.947
I choose today to do all that.

00:40:15.947 --> 00:40:18.968
" That's what He said.

00:40:31.600 --> 00:40:31.920
And He was obedient.

00:40:46.460 --> 00:40:46.810
The Bible says He became obedient unto death, to the point where He said, "My Father, My Father, why have You forsaken Me?

00:40:46.810 --> 00:40:52.409
" Because the sin was so bad on Him that God had to turn His back on Him because it was so heavy.

00:40:52.409 --> 00:40:58.800
He couldn't look at Him because it was that dirty, it was that bad, because He took everything, sickness, everything.

00:40:58.800 --> 00:41:00.720
He became obedient unto death.

00:41:00.720 --> 00:41:01.964
He didn't know death.

00:41:01.964 --> 00:41:06.820
He had to receive it by faith, because He didn't even know.

00:41:06.820 --> 00:41:13.839
He knew how to walk in healing, He knew how to walk in prosperity, He knew how to do everything, but He had to receive all that by faith.

00:41:14.799 --> 00:41:15.760
"I receive sickness.

00:41:15.760 --> 00:41:17.634
I receive it.

00:41:27.149 --> 00:41:27.359
" And He had to do it by faith because He had never done it before.

00:41:27.359 --> 00:41:32.800
He knew no sickness, He knew no sin, He knew none of it, and He had to yield Himself to it.

00:41:32.800 --> 00:41:35.623
Say, "God, I take it for them.

00:41:35.623 --> 00:41:39.080
" But He did it for you, and He did it for me.

00:41:39.080 --> 00:41:41.199
He did it all for us.

00:41:41.199 --> 00:41:42.199
Galatians 3:13.

00:41:51.440 --> 00:41:51.840
That Christ has redeemed us from the curse of the law.

00:42:05.808 --> 00:42:06.112
He became sickness.

00:42:06.112 --> 00:42:07.328
He became disease.

00:42:07.328 --> 00:42:09.566
He was wounded for our transgressions.

00:42:09.566 --> 00:42:11.520
He was bruised for our iniquities.

00:42:16.500 --> 00:42:17.280
The chastisement of our peace was upon Him, and with His stripes, we are healed.

00:42:17.280 --> 00:42:18.059
He took it for you.

00:42:18.059 --> 00:42:20.308
He took it for me.

00:42:25.060 --> 00:42:25.280
And He said, "I become obedient unto this.

00:42:25.720 --> 00:42:26.160
I yield myself.

